Tables:
    - books
        - ID
        - Title
        - Author
        - ISBN
        - Category
        - LoanID
        - BookNumber --> Join with bookshelf (?)

    - loans
        - BookID
        - MemberID
        - Taken
        - Returned (nullable)

    - members
        - MembersID
        - FirstName
        - LastName
        - Address
        - Phone
        - Birth
        - Gender
        - Email
    ____
    - bookshelf
        - BookshelfID
        - BookIDs
        - Category
